name: Robin Dettman
text:
Always great sandwiches.  Fresh veggies.  Great service. Good food. And the new menu is a great addition.
Had a pizza. Not a fan of the pizza sauce though. Doesn't taste the same b4 new menu.

name: Barak Pinnon
text: Quick-service, the girl serving was friendly üëç

name: Robyn Mings
text: Got 2 footlongs one toasted and the other heated the meat was still cold when we ate them like they just came out of refrigerator they keep getting worse very disappointed

name: Jazzy
text: I love subway but this time around it took entirely way to long for the guy to make my sandwich, there was sauce everywhere and my sandwich was split in the top of the bread which made a huge mess when I unwrapped it.

name: JB Brown
text: There are now more Subways  than there are Macdonalds.  That is a good thing. They always seem to have fresh crispy  vegetables. Gift Cards don't work at this Subway.

name: Billy turnbull
text: Great place to get a sandwich

name: Nene Smith
text: A roach or water bug or whatever it is or was. It was in my salad. I'm very displeased with subway

name: Denise R
text: BMT'S are always the way to go!
